        <footnote id="F9">The initial exercise price of the Warrants is $7 per share of Common Stock, subject to adjustment as set forth in the Form of Warrant Certificate, filed as Exhibit 4.2 to the Issuer's Current Report on Form 8-K filed with the SEC on September 6, 2011 (the &quot;Warrant Certificate&quot;).</footnote>
